properties.name: Findhorn
properties.description: Posted by JohnnyspanglerForresOne of the most magical places in the world. I spent one month a year here every year for about five years of my life.

properties.name: First Girlfriend
properties.description: Posted by JohnnyspanglerHere is the house of my first girlfriend, and yes, I still lived all the way over in seattle. We were together (though not in proximity) for three years. Eventualy her family moved to seattle, just in time for me to move to TN.

properties.name: Home
properties.description: Posted by Johnnyspangler4440 190th Ave se 98027No matter where I live in my life this house will always be called home. I grew up here and my heart will always partly be there. We visited the lake almost every day in the summer and the trees around my house were my jungle gym. I knew this neighborhood like the back of my hand.

properties.name: My Apt.
properties.description: Posted by Johnnyspangler110 w ridgewood ave 37415Here is my Apt. I moved here in the summer of 2005. the very first time I ever lived alone

properties.name: My trip to Sydney
properties.description: Posted by Johnnyspanglersydney opera houseSome where around this down town area we stayed on our trip to sydney. We visited the opera house and the Art Museum. We also got to travel all over the country here and see many beautiful palces.

properties.name: Rex and Sherries
properties.description: Posted by JohnnyspanglerMy first home away from home. I stayed here two years while taking the acting program. I was part of the family and at the same time very much on my own. It was a perfect transition

properties.name: WSU 4-H Bonney Lake Challenge Course
properties.description: Posted by Johnnyspanglerbonney lake WAI spent a year here as an americorps member. I got to lead groups on the challenge courses they have in the 120 acres of forest. I developed a environmental education program for the course.

properties.name: Where I met Jessie
properties.description: Posted by JohnnyspanglerThe VaudeVille Cafe. My first job in TN (as an actor in the kids show) and where I first layed eyes on my beautiful Jessie. After love at first sight (and leaving her "speachless") we have been together since.

properties.name: Where Jessie will be moving too
properties.description: Posted by JohnnyspanglerSantiagoyes it\'s true. Jessie will be moving all the way down here. A beautiful place I hear and i look forward to an excuse to visit :)
